## 1. Global Layout & CSS Rules (MANDATORY)

You **MUST** inject the following CSS at the very top of `app.py` to remove Streamlit's default massive padding:

```python
st.set_page_config(layout="wide", page_title="PDF2PDF")

st.markdown("""
    <style>
        /* Remove top header padding */
        .block-container {
            padding-top: 1rem !important;
            padding-bottom: 0rem !important;
            max-width: 95% !important;
        }
        /* Compact headers */
        h1, h2, h3 {
            margin-top: 0rem !important;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem !important;
            padding-top: 0rem !important;
        }
        /* Reduce element spacing */
        .element-container {
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem !important;
        }
        /* Center Upload Box */
        div[data-testid="stFileUploader"] {
            margin: auto;
            width: 80%;
        }
    </style>
""", unsafe_allow_html=True)
```
